data.description: Space and storage abound in the 3-bedroom Baker plan from LGI Homes. This two-story home provides a true retreat for the largest of families, showcasing a spacious great room perfect for entertaining. Additionally, homeowners will enjoy access to the neighborhood park featuring picnic seating, open green space and walking paths.
